===Etymology===
{{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|pece||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|peece|lang=xno}}, {{term|peice}} et al. and {{etyl|fro}} {{term|pece}}, {{term|piece|lang=fro}} et al., apparently from {{etyl|LL.|en}} *{{term||pettia|lang=la}}, *{{term||pettium||lang=la}}. Ultimate origin uncertain; perhaps from {{etyl|xtg|en}} (compare {{etyl|cy|-}} {{term|peth|lang=cy}}, {{etyl|br|-}} {{term|pez||thing|lang=br}}, {{etyl|ga|-}} {{term|cuid|lang=ga||part}}).

